&lt;p&gt;Meddygfa Cwm Rhymni Practice requires Prescribing Pharmacist to head the medicine management at the practice. Part or full time considered. The practice has 13,000 patients and operates between 3 sites in Rhymney, New Tredegar &amp; Deri utilizing Vision IT system.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The team comprises of 7 partners, 1 Salaried GP, 2 x ANP, 1 NCN Pharmacist, 4 Practice Nurses, 3 HCA &amp; 3 Prescribing Clerks, all supported by a team of administrative staff.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are also a training practice for registrars, F2&#39;s, Year 5&#39;s &amp; Year 1&#39;s.&lt;/p&gt;
